main event: A sighting of an unidentified object in Zionsville, Indiana on August 11, 1965.
interesting points: The object was observed for a duration of 10-15 seconds., The observation was made optically and visually., The sighting occurred at noon time., The course of the object was directed south., There was no physical evidence or photographs provided.
witness description: The witness provided a detailed questionnaire about the observation.
